  "engines": ["Oxidize"],
  "description": "The sound of a piano recorded to cassette tape 40 years ago. Triangle wave for soft attack, TapeSat corrosion, tape mid-scoop erosion, gentle wow and flutter. ageOffset 0.3 means the tape is already old before you play the first note — preserveAmount 0.6 ensures it never turns destructive.",
